Details about the operation were kept secret for a long time, the film has been made from the memories of Tony Mendez.
Affleck’s film is a unique combination of several genres.
On the one hand, a realistic political thriller; on the other hand, a so-called "caper movie", the story of an episode that went well, a deception (an example can be the series Ocean's Eleven).
We find on one side well-documented sequences of Tehran.In the credit sequence emblematic photographs of the time of the events are shown, which were shaped in the same way in the film; there are not many differences in this regard.
On the other hand, typical Hollywood scenes somewhat lighter, marked by irony and a slight exaggeration.
